<seg id="2082">In & quantaplus; the working area is divided into three areas: global, local and project related. this distinction concerns a number of components in & quantaplus;.</seg>
<seg id="2083">Global elements are available for everyone who uses & quantaplus; it stores everything that is marked globally in the shared folder structure of & quantaplus; this allows the group of administrators to secure different tool tracks, actions and patterns in the global tree, which are then available to everyone in a multi-user environment on the system.</seg>
